|-----------|----------------------------|----------------------------|---------|
|**A**      |Pass with 1.37% buffer      |Pass with **1.88% buffer** ✓|AAA (sf) |
|**B-Dfrd** |Pass comfortably            |Pass comfortably            |AA (sf)  |
|**C-Dfrd** |Pass at A-                  |Pass at **A** ✓             |A (sf)   |
|**D-Dfrd** |Pass at BBB- (CE constraint)|Pass at **BBB+** ✓          |BBB+ (sf)|
